com.facebook.litho.sections.common

Class RenderWithHideItemHandlerEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.litho.sections.common.RenderWithHideItemHandlerEvent

  • public class RenderWithHideItemHandlerEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    An Event that gets triggered by a HideableDataDiffSectionSpec to render the edges of the connection.

    RenderWithHideItemHandlerEvent is triggered when the com.facebook.litho.sections.annotations.DiffSectionSpec is generating the ChangeSet.

    This means that when RenderWithHideItemHandlerEvent is handled, the components are not inserted into the adapter yet.
